Paper: hep-th/9601029

Date: 1996-01-09

Title: Microscopic Origin of the Bekenstein-Hawking Entropy

Authors: A. Strominger and C. Vafa

Comments: 12 pages. Relatively minor corrections and additions to discussion

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B379 (1996) 99-104

The Bekenstein-Hawking area-entropy relation $S_{BH}=A/4$ is derived for aclass of five-dimensional extremal black holes in string theory by counting thedegeneracy of BPS soliton bound states.